# kit_demo exercise: menu -> play, walk the player with a held d-pad,
# stamp two random blocks (A) with verified saves, back to menu.
# Emulator frames (bundled BIOS ~60-frame bootstrap).
90   screenshot bin/kitdemo_menu.png
100  tap        A
130  screenshot bin/kitdemo_play.png
140  press      RIGHT
190  release    RIGHT
170  press      DOWN
210  release    DOWN
215  tap        A
230  tap        A
250  screenshot bin/kitdemo_stamped.png
260  tap        B
280  screenshot bin/kitdemo_menu_back.png
